    "desc": "Oceanside Glass & Tile® is the manufacturer of the Oceanside Compatible™ family of fusible glass products — an expansive range of fusible sheet glass and coordinating glass accessories.",
    "navbar": "Glass Tile\nArt Glass\nXS Studio\n.cls-1,.cls-2{fill:none !important;stroke:#050101;stroke-miterlimit:10;stroke-width:12px;}.cls-2{stroke-linecap:round;}search\nSearch\n.cls-1{fill:none;stroke:#4f687b;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:12px;} .cls-1:hover{stroke: #222} cart",
    "text": "Glass Tile\nArt Glass\nXS Studio\n.cls-1,.cls-2{fill:none !important;stroke:#050101;stroke-miterlimit:10;stroke-width:12px;}.cls-2{stroke-linecap:round;}search\nSearch\n.cls-1{fill:none;stroke:#4f687b;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:12px;} .cls-1:hover{stroke: #222} cart\nProducts\nCatalogs\nPurchasing\nResources\nAbout Us\n\nCOLOR FOR BLOWING\nAnnouncing a robust line of Oceanside Compatible™ Color Bars Available NOW!\nColor Bar Collection\nGlass Products\nOceanside Glass & Tile® is the manufacturer of the Oceanside Compatible™ family of fusible glass products — an expansive range of fusible sheet glass and coordinating glass accessories. Learn more.\nSheet Glass\nGlass Frit\nGlass Stringers, Noodles & Rods\nGlass Blowing Products\nGlass Packs\nEducation and Resources\nOceanside Glass & Tile is committed to providing useful tools to assist you as you create your own beautiful glass art — including information, support, and inspiration.\n\nWe also provide extensive firing and annealing schedules for use with our products.\nFiring Schedules\nInspiration Gallery\nProject Concepts\nBasic Fusing Tips\nJoin our #GlassFam!\nSign up to get all the exclusive perks like being among the first to know when our next Fusers Reserve™ glass launches, new product sneak peeks, deals & more!\nBy entering your phone number and submitting this form, you consent to receive marketing text messages (such as promotion codes and cart reminders) fromOceanside Glass & Tile at the number provided, including messages sent by autodialer. Consent is not a condition of any purchase. Message and data rates may apply. Message frequency varies. You can unsubscribe at any time by replying STOP or clicking the unsubscribe link (where available) in one of our messages. View our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.\nSign up\nOceanside Glasstile World Headquarters\n5858 Edison Place\nCarlsbad, CA 92008\n760-929-4041\nartglass@glasstile.com\nAbout Us\nContact Us\nFAQ\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms of Service\nRefund Policy\nShipping Policy\nOceanside Glasstile Co. © 2020, All Rights Reserved",
